nners-adab","tag-obedience-al-taah","tag-parables-amthal","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9SD","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":27043,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/16\/pleased-allah-muhammad-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":37983,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: I am pleased with Allah, Muhammad, Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says when he enters the evening, \u2018I am pleased with Allah as a Lord, with Islam as a religion, and with Muhammad as a prophet,\u2019 it will be a duty upon Allah to please him.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11062,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/always-believers-obedient\/","url_meta":{"origin":37983,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Faith: There will always be righteous believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu 'Inabah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah will continue to cultivate in this religion those He uses to act in obedience to Him.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 8 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0639\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0